        <%= image_tag "extended_away1.png", class:"imagesportfolio" %>
        <div class="card-product-infos cardsportfolio">
          <h3 class="mb-5">Extended Away</h3>
          <p>A web app designed for people who are going to travel and need someone to take care of their homes. Our mission is to provide a simple, intuitive way for Homeowners and Caretakers to interact and get things done, faster. </p>
